{"tid":2363183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發！WhatsApp 電話、照片群組邀竟可從 Google 搜出來！","createTime":"2021-01-12T04:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T07:08:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"52bfbd6ae2802d87f8d94b147230503a59730054","tid":2363183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp 的 Group 群組功能一般也是非公開的，要有別人的邀請才可加入。如果你的連結竟然可透過 Googe 搜出來，而有連結的人都可以加入這些私人群組，那麼你覺得會安全嗎？<br />\n<br />\n資訊安全研究人員 Rajshekhar Rajaharia 向網媒 Gadget360 指出，超過 1500 個 WhatsApp 群組邀請連結被 Google 搜索器 Index，而這些 Index 看來是近期進行。根據 Gadget360 的追查，被 Index 了的 WhatsApp 群組連結部份是一些分享色情內容的群組，也有一些是興趣相關群組及特定的社區群組。當中更看到一些用戶名稱，例如 Bangla 及 Marathi。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUjc12G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUjc12G.jpg&h=cc6dfe25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了群組連結，Gadgets 360 更發現 WhatsApp 用戶 Profile 資料可從 Google 搜出來，當中包括電話號碼、Status 及照片。當時 Google 已對超過 5000 個 WhatsApp Profile 進行 Index。<br />\n<br />\nRajshekhar Rajaharia 指出，WhatsApp 沒有在 robots.txt 加入 <a href=\"http://chat.whatsapp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchat.whatsapp.com&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=41ca6fa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">chat.whatsapp.com</a>  及 <a href=\"http://api.whatsapp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.whatsapp.com&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=85c38d74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">api.whatsapp.com</a>，令 Google 將當中的內容進行 Index。其實 WhatsApp 資料被 Googe 「搜出來」也不是首次，到早在 2019 年 11 月 WhatsApp 也曾出現過相同的問題，只是後來修正了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/01/12/whatsapp-content-indexed-by-google/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2021%2F01%2F12%2Fwhatsapp-content-indexed-by-google%2F&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=22ce5dac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/01/12/whatsapp-content-indexed-by-google/</a>"},{"pid":"de287001a2db01e9a06c89f02eb3015030aa2063","tid":2363183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435defb043bd8c6c44603c1b21cea19c62a42485","tid":2363183,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"其實 WhatsApp 資料被 Googe 「搜出來」也不是首次，到早在 2019 年 11 月 WhatsApp 也曾出現過相同的問題，只是後來修正了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能上次係Test，今次永恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6972798c8a8abf22a9ce46a341be2c295e41679f","tid":2363183,"uid":88263,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得你呢個群組係好不健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95f0a3b06a22b7134fc5b0b0f179772697e4414","tid":2363183,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"朱西狗等睇步林早洩後塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd47044ba3f8f7d5610186ba20e571f1084f6ee7","tid":2363183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.p